Join me, Kim Goodburn,
on this historic new journey.

4
00:00:25,760 --> 00:00:28,600
This is <i>The Face Men Thailand Season 4</i>.

5
00:00:33,280 --> 00:00:35,960
<i>Last week, Team Mentor Pancake-Ananda</i>

6
00:00:36,040 --> 00:00:38,720
<i>executed a flawless campaign strategy</i>

7
00:00:38,800 --> 00:00:40,960
