8
00:00:41,040 --> 00:00:44,160
Kimhan from Team Mentor Pancake-Ananda.

9
00:00:44,240 --> 00:00:46,360
So this is what victory smells like.

10
00:00:46,440 --> 00:00:47,800
Remember this.

11
00:00:47,880 --> 00:00:51,040
<i>Forcing Mentor Off</i>
<i>to send Mew to the Black Room.</i>

12
00:00:51,120 --> 00:00:53,920
<i>While Mentor Mile sent Gluf</i>

13
00:00:54,000 --> 00:00:56,080
<i>since he can't walk the Final Walk anyway.</i>

14
