I'm no longer eligible, so he sent me in.

15
00:00:59,040 --> 00:01:00,080
Is that so?

16
00:01:00,160 --> 00:01:01,120
Do you want to save him?

17
00:01:02,640 --> 00:01:03,960
You can go get him.

18
00:01:04,040 --> 00:01:07,400
<i>Gluf was ultimately saved</i>
<i>by Mentor Jes and Bible.</i>

19
00:01:07,480 --> 00:01:10,760
<i>And Mew was finally eliminated.</i>

20
00:01:10,840 --> 00:01:12,920
Gluf, you're a survivor.

21
00:01:13,000 --> 00:01:16,440
What kind of amulet do you have?
The Sacred Gluf?

22
00:01:46,720 --> 00:01:49,240
<i>The winner</i>
<i>of </i>The Face Men Thailand Season 4

23
00:01:49,320 --> 00:01:51,720
