<i>with Vaseline Thailand.</i>

26
00:01:59,040 --> 00:02:02,600
<i>Plus, he'll receive</i>
<i>Vaseline SPF50+ PA++++,</i>

27
00:02:02,680 --> 00:02:05,920
<i>Gluta Hyaluronic Acid,</i>
<i>Photoage Defense UV Serum</i>

28
00:02:06,000 --> 00:02:07,800
<i>free for an entire year.</i>

29
00:02:07,880 --> 00:02:10,080
<i>He will also collaborate with AXE</i>

30
00:02:10,160 --> 00:02:13,280
<i>and receive a year's supply</i>
<i>of personal care products.</i>

31
00:02:13,360 --> 00:02:16,760
<i>Bearbeary, only the wearers feel it.</i>

32
00:02:16,840 --> 00:02:20,640
<i>Premium wear for every style,</i>
<i>featuring top design and innovation.</i>

33
00:02:20,720 --> 00:02:22,880
<i>They'll award a 100,000-baht gift voucher.</i>

34
00:02:22,960 --> 00:02:27,200
<i>Strive for perfection</i>
<i>with a membership to Hotman Fitness.</i>

35
00:02:27,280 --> 00:02:30,440
<i>Including an 18-month</i>
<i>personal training program.</i>

36
00:02:30,520 --> 00:02:33,840
<i>Plus a 200,000-baht package</i>
<i>from V Design Clinic.</i>

37
00:02:33,920 --> 00:02:36,440
<i>Get ready to step onto the national screen</i>

38
00:02:36,520 --> 00:02:39,480
<i>through a collaboration</i>
<i>with Channel 3 HD, Thailand.</i>

39
00:02:39,560 --> 00:02:43,600
<i>And sign an acting contract</i>
<i>with Kantana Group Public Company Limited,</i>

40
00:02:43,680 --> 00:02:46,160
<i>Thailand's leading producer</i>
<i>of dramas and films.</i>

41
00:03:46,320 --> 00:03:47,600
Hello, everyone.

42
00:03:47,680 --> 00:03:48,920
- Hello!
- Hello!

43
00:03:49,000 --> 00:03:51,040
Welcome back to <i>The Face Men Thailand</i>,

44
00:03:51,120 --> 00:03:52,880
Week six!

45
00:03:55,240 --> 00:03:57,600
Wow, time flies, doesn't it?

46
00:03:57,680 --> 00:03:59,480
Let's leave all the negativity behind.

47
00:03:59,560 --> 00:04:01,480
We're living in the present now.

48
00:04:01,560 --> 00:04:03,400
My eyes are on the prize.

49
00:04:03,480 --> 00:04:06,560
By now, I believe
you all have enough experience

50
00:04:06,640 --> 00:04:08,760
to tackle whatever comes your way.

51
00:04:08,840 --> 00:04:10,760
If it's a master class or a campaign,

52
00:04:10,840 --> 00:04:12,880
you're ready for the challenge.

53
00:04:12,960 --> 00:04:15,720
Today, we have two mentors

54
00:04:15,800 --> 00:04:19,640
here to guide you
through the master class.

55
00:04:19,720 --> 00:04:22,079
Give it up
for Mentor Pancake and Mentor Jes.

56
00:04:28,800 --> 00:04:30,920
All right. We have a special twist today.

57
00:04:31,000 --> 00:04:34,400
We're jumping straight
into the master class challenge.

58
00:04:35,720 --> 00:04:37,400
Oh, straight to the brief.

59
00:04:37,480 --> 00:04:40,400
No class today?
Guess we're pros now, no learning needed.

60
00:04:40,480 --> 00:04:43,280
I have no idea.
This is totally unpredictable.

61
00:04:44,160 --> 00:04:46,080
Today, our contestants

62
00:04:46,160 --> 00:04:49,640
must use every skill
they've learned so far

63
00:04:49,720 --> 00:04:52,000
to win this master class.

64
00:04:52,080 --> 00:04:56,360
To reveal today's brief, let's welcome
the man bringing us the challenge.

65
00:04:56,440 --> 00:04:58,320
Welcome Pongpisut Limgul,

66
00:04:58,400 --> 00:05:02,040
Commercial Lead for Personal Care
Thailand, Cambodia, and Laos at Unilever!

67
00:05:07,360 --> 00:05:09,440
PONGPISUT LIMGUL

68
00:05:09,520 --> 00:05:13,760
Oab, what kind of challenge
do you have for the guys today?

69
00:05:13,840 --> 00:05:16,560
Today's brief is "The Gravity Scent."

70
00:05:16,640 --> 00:05:19,160
You'll be shooting
a reverse fashion video,

71
00:05:19,240 --> 00:05:22,200
inspired by
the AXE Fine Fragrance Collection TVC

72
00:05:22,280 --> 00:05:23,200
starring Mark Tuan.

73
00:05:23,280 --> 00:05:25,040
What exactly is The Gravity Scent?

74
00:05:25,120 --> 00:05:28,320
It's the scent of our AXE Fine Fragrance,

75
00:05:28,400 --> 00:05:29,680
Blue Lavender.

76
00:05:29,760 --> 00:05:31,640
Co-created with world-class perfumers,

77
00:05:31,720 --> 00:05:33,880
for a premium fragrance
that lasts 72 hours.

78
00:05:33,960 --> 00:05:36,080
A scent so magnetic, it defies gravity.

79
00:05:36,160 --> 00:05:37,520
Essentially,

80
00:05:37,600 --> 00:05:39,880
this AXE Fine Fragrance Collection

81
00:05:39,960 --> 00:05:42,920
has an "Anti-Gravity" effect.

82
00:05:43,000 --> 00:05:46,840
In the commercial,
Mark Tuan exudes charm and confidence.

83
00:05:46,920 --> 00:05:48,920
Most importantly, he's being himself.

84
00:05:49,000 --> 00:05:51,480
He attracts and defies gravity.

85
00:05:51,560 --> 00:05:55,360
Everything around him
is drawn straight to him.

86
00:05:55,440 --> 00:05:57,880
The concept is simple,
but execution is difficult.

87
00:05:57,960 --> 00:05:59,720
You just have to go for it.

88
00:06:00,480 --> 00:06:02,840
For today's reverse fashion video,

89
00:06:02,920 --> 00:06:07,800
we're honored to have a top fashion
photographer in Thailand and Asia.

90
00:06:07,880 --> 00:06:10,720
He'll also be joining us
as a guest judge today.

91
00:06:10,800 --> 00:06:13,640
Welcome Nat Prakobsantisuk!

92
00:06:20,040 --> 00:06:22,480
NAT PRAKOBSANTISUK
TOP FASHION PHOTOGRAPHER

93
00:06:22,560 --> 00:06:25,480
Nat, for today's reverse fashion video,

94
00:06:25,560 --> 00:06:27,040
how are we shooting this?

95
00:06:27,120 --> 00:06:29,960
The guys will have to walk backward.

96
00:06:30,040 --> 00:06:31,320
Meanwhile,

97
00:06:31,400 --> 00:06:34,640
the prop team will shower them
with flower petals.

98
00:06:34,720 --> 00:06:37,280
We'll then edit the footage in reverse.

99
00:06:37,360 --> 00:06:39,240
The real challenge here

100
00:06:39,320 --> 00:06:41,920
is pulling off that backward walk.

101
00:06:42,000 --> 00:06:46,160
You need to calculate
and control every muscle.

102
00:06:46,240 --> 00:06:49,600
And place your feet exactly
like you're walking forward.

103
00:06:49,680 --> 00:06:52,320
Walking backward,
but making it look forward.

104
00:06:52,400 --> 00:06:54,560
How on earth do you pull that off?

105
00:06:54,640 --> 00:06:56,520
Easier said than done, right?

106
00:06:56,600 --> 00:07:00,920
While you're walking backward,
you still have to serve it to the camera

107
00:07:01,000 --> 00:07:03,680
and exude absolute charisma.

108
00:07:03,760 --> 00:07:08,560
Make the audience feel
that your charm defies gravity,

109
00:07:08,640 --> 00:07:12,080
so much so that objects float towards you.

110
00:07:12,160 --> 00:07:13,960
I can barely walk straight.

111
00:07:14,040 --> 00:07:16,320
I trip all the time,
and now I have to walk backwards?

112
00:07:16,400 --> 00:07:19,400
But today, we have
another very special guest judge.

113
00:07:19,480 --> 00:07:22,200
Please welcome Master Mentor Adam!

114
00:07:25,920 --> 00:07:27,760
- Hello.
- Hello.

115
00:07:29,280 --> 00:07:32,120
M.R. CHALERMCHATRI YUKOL

116
00:07:32,200 --> 00:07:35,040
Having Master Mentor Adam
as a judge today,

117
00:07:35,120 --> 00:07:40,240
I just hope the odds are in my favor.

118
00:07:40,760 --> 00:07:44,080
Adam, any advice for the guys
in today's master class?

119
00:07:44,160 --> 00:07:46,640
I want you to enjoy it. Have fun with it.

120
00:07:46,720 --> 00:07:50,920
In past challenges,
you've all looked so stiff and stressed.

121
00:07:51,000 --> 00:07:53,240
I get it, but you need to loosen up.

122
00:07:53,320 --> 00:07:56,040
If you have fun,
your true potential will shine through.

123
00:07:56,120 --> 00:07:58,080
You all made it this far for a reason.

124
00:07:58,160 --> 00:08:00,920
The question is, how do you show it off?

125
00:08:01,000 --> 00:08:06,040
You can only deliver
if you genuinely enjoy the moment.

126
00:08:06,640 --> 00:08:09,360
All right, before we kick off
today's master class,

127
00:08:09,440 --> 00:08:12,840
let's get some quick advice
from our mentors.

128
00:08:12,920 --> 00:08:15,440
Mentor Jes, any words of wisdom
for the guys?

129
00:08:15,520 --> 00:08:16,480
This is tough.

130
00:08:16,560 --> 00:08:18,040
- It's incredibly hard.
- True.

131
00:08:18,120 --> 00:08:21,680
You have to be hyper-aware
of your space and your purpose.

132
00:08:21,760 --> 00:08:23,440
And what you're feeling.

133
00:08:23,520 --> 00:08:27,320
You need a clear storyline.
Everyone's will be completely different.

134
00:08:27,400 --> 00:08:29,920
That uniqueness
is where your true charm lies.

135
00:08:30,000 --> 00:08:33,400
Figure out exactly what vibe
you want to project.

136
00:08:33,480 --> 00:08:35,679
And own it with confidence.

137
00:08:35,760 --> 00:08:40,360
Stay sharp on every single step.
You have to control every backward stride.

138
00:08:40,440 --> 00:08:44,360
Control your body, your face,
everything simultaneously.

139
00:08:44,440 --> 00:08:47,600
No dead eyes. Stay focused.
Keep the story alive in your mind.

140
00:08:48,400 --> 00:08:49,640
Short and sweet.

141
00:08:49,720 --> 00:08:52,680
"Stay sharp on every single step."
That felt personal.

142
00:08:53,880 --> 00:08:56,000
To sum up today's master class brief,

143
00:08:56,080 --> 00:08:57,440
"The Gravity Scent,"

144
00:08:57,520 --> 00:09:02,120
all contestants will be shooting
a reverse fashion video today.

145
00:09:02,200 --> 00:09:04,760
You have to walk the runway backward.

146
00:09:04,840 --> 00:09:09,000
And you only get two takes.

147
00:09:09,600 --> 00:09:12,760
Each take consists
of two continuous scenes.

148
00:09:12,840 --> 00:09:15,720
Scene one, deliver our tagline,

149
00:09:15,800 --> 00:09:18,560
"AXE Fine Fragrance Collection,

150
00:09:18,640 --> 00:09:22,360
premium scent,
unexpected 72-hour protection."

151
00:09:22,440 --> 00:09:24,440
Right after that is scene two.

152
00:09:24,520 --> 00:09:28,760
You need to strut out,
looking like a quintessential AXE guy.

153
00:09:28,840 --> 00:09:32,280
Finally, the footage will be reversed

154
00:09:32,360 --> 00:09:36,960
to create a final cut that showcases
the magnetic pull of the fragrance.

155
00:09:37,040 --> 00:09:39,960
Making objects around you defy gravity.

156
00:09:40,040 --> 00:09:42,880
The tagline is in Thai again today.

157
00:09:43,840 --> 00:09:44,800
It will be tough.

158
00:09:44,880 --> 00:09:46,120
But I really want to win.

159
00:09:48,400 --> 00:09:49,360
Are you ready?

160
00:09:49,440 --> 00:09:50,560
- Ready!
- Ready!

161
00:09:50,640 --> 00:09:52,280
Then get ready for

162
00:09:52,360 --> 00:09:54,480
The Gravity Scent master class!

163
00:09:58,160 --> 00:10:01,440
I'm ready. I won't let the pressure
get me. Just enjoy and have fun.

164
00:10:01,520 --> 00:10:03,440
I'll try my best. Going all in.

165
00:10:03,520 --> 00:10:05,040
That's the game plan.

166
00:10:05,120 --> 00:10:06,280
Wish me luck.

167
00:10:15,840 --> 00:10:18,400
Welcome back
to The Gravity Scent master class.

168
00:10:18,480 --> 00:10:20,160
In today's brief,

169
00:10:20,240 --> 00:10:22,760
the contestants need to walk the runway

170
00:10:22,840 --> 00:10:26,760
to showcase
a fragrance that defies gravity,

171
00:10:26,840 --> 00:10:28,360
with AXE Blue Lavender.

172
00:10:28,440 --> 00:10:31,440
Let's bring out our first contestant.

173
00:10:31,520 --> 00:10:32,920
Give it up for Bonus.

174
00:10:33,000 --> 00:10:34,160
- Oh, wow!
- Nice.

175
00:10:34,240 --> 00:10:35,480
- Go ahead.
- Oh, wow!

176
00:10:35,560 --> 00:10:36,400
So damn handsome.

177
00:10:36,480 --> 00:10:39,000
Don't forget, you only get two takes.

178
00:10:39,960 --> 00:10:42,280
I went in first,
and that took some pressure off.

179
00:10:42,360 --> 00:10:44,680
I just went in, did a little dance,
and loosened up.

180
00:10:44,760 --> 00:10:46,240
I showed them everything I've got.

181
00:10:46,320 --> 00:10:48,720
First take. Whenever you're ready.

182
00:10:51,040 --> 00:10:54,280
AXE Fine Fragrance Collection,

183
00:10:54,360 --> 00:10:58,200
premium scent,
unexpected 72-hour protection.

184
00:10:59,800 --> 00:11:01,720
Is his pace too slow?

185
00:11:01,800 --> 00:11:04,080
- It looks like he's creeping.
- Okay, all right.

186
00:11:04,160 --> 00:11:06,680
It looks like he's just sliding backwards.

187
00:11:06,760 --> 00:11:08,760
Should he stride instead?

188
00:11:12,960 --> 00:11:14,000
Cut!

189
00:11:14,080 --> 00:11:15,320
It will play in reverse.

190
00:11:15,400 --> 00:11:18,160
Oh, if he throws it,
it will reverse back into his hand.

191
00:11:18,240 --> 00:11:20,760
- Like he grabs it. Yes.
- Like this.

192
00:11:20,840 --> 00:11:22,720
- Like it flew back to his hand!
- Yes!

193
00:11:22,800 --> 00:11:24,200
Clever! I like it.

194
00:11:24,280 --> 00:11:27,240
One last take, Bonus.
Whenever you're ready. Action!

195
00:11:27,840 --> 00:11:30,480
AXE Fine Fragrance Collection,

196
00:11:31,200 --> 00:11:34,760
premium scent,
unexpected 72-hour protection.

197
00:11:34,840 --> 00:11:36,440
His delivery is so confident.

198
00:11:36,520 --> 00:11:37,760
- Nailed it.
- So confident.

199
00:11:37,840 --> 00:11:39,320
- Great delivery.
- Good pacing.

200
00:11:40,840 --> 00:11:44,440
With his whole look,
I think he's a perfect fit for AXE.

201
00:11:44,520 --> 00:11:48,440
He's one of my top picks.
He totally embodies the product.

202
00:11:48,520 --> 00:11:50,360
Let's move on to the next contestant.

203
00:11:50,440 --> 00:11:52,600
Donut. First take.

204
00:11:52,680 --> 00:11:55,480
Three, two, one, action!

205
00:11:59,880 --> 00:12:01,480
AXE Fine Fragrance Collection,

206
00:12:02,080 --> 00:12:05,080
premium scent,
unexpected 72-hour protection.

207
00:12:05,160 --> 00:12:07,320
- Dead.
- The product blocked your face.

208
00:12:08,640 --> 00:12:11,960
I didn't realize it in the first take.
I just went with the pose

209
00:12:12,040 --> 00:12:13,720
that felt the most natural.

210
00:12:13,800 --> 00:12:16,200
I chose that pose,
but ended up blocking my face.

211
00:12:16,800 --> 00:12:18,600
Lesson learned, for sure.

212
00:12:18,680 --> 00:12:22,120
You only have one take left, Donut.
Whenever you're ready. Action!

213
00:12:22,200 --> 00:12:25,400
AXE Fine Fragrance Collection,

214
00:12:25,480 --> 00:12:28,400
premium scent,
unexpected 72-hour protection.

215
00:12:29,360 --> 00:12:31,920
This brief really suits Donut.

216
00:12:32,000 --> 00:12:35,640
He's giving pure edge,
masculinity, and cool vibes.

217
00:12:35,720 --> 00:12:38,600
I really see his potential.

218
00:12:38,680 --> 00:12:41,760
- Yes, great confidence.
- Better than I thought.

219
00:12:41,840 --> 00:12:43,160
Donut killed it today.

220
00:12:43,240 --> 00:12:46,880
I didn't expect him to pull this off.
He was so sharp and focused.

221
00:12:46,960 --> 00:12:49,360
Not a single moment
of panic or hesitation.

222
00:12:49,440 --> 00:12:51,200
Next up, Leo!

223
00:12:51,280 --> 00:12:52,920
Here comes the <i>Oppa</i>.

224
00:12:55,840 --> 00:12:57,000
Hello.

225
00:12:59,880 --> 00:13:02,640
AXE Fine Fragrance Collection,

226
00:13:02,720 --> 00:13:06,440
premium scent,
unexpected 72-hour protection.

227
00:13:06,520 --> 00:13:10,560
<i>Oppa </i>nailed the tagline! I'm thrilled.
Was his pronunciation perfect? No.

228
00:13:10,640 --> 00:13:12,240
But it was cute in <i>Oppa</i>'s style.

229
00:13:12,320 --> 00:13:14,760
Damn, he designed the walk.

230
00:13:14,840 --> 00:13:18,080
I thought he would struggle
with the lines, but his walk…

231
00:13:18,160 --> 00:13:21,120
No, no. Take two will be better, trust me.

232
00:13:23,280 --> 00:13:25,560
Wow, our <i>Oppa </i>is full of surprises today.

233
00:13:30,200 --> 00:13:33,160
AXE Fine Fragrance Collection,

234
00:13:33,680 --> 00:13:36,760
premium scent,
unexpected 72-hour protection.

235
00:13:36,840 --> 00:13:41,600
He has a gorgeous smile.
Once he relaxed, he completely delivered.

236
00:13:42,200 --> 00:13:44,760
Leo really hit it out of the park here.

237
00:13:44,840 --> 00:13:47,600
And his natural charm
really shone through.

238
00:13:47,680 --> 00:13:50,440
I think Leo is a strong contender.

239
00:13:51,160 --> 00:13:53,360
Fourth up, please welcome Gluf.

240
00:13:53,440 --> 00:13:55,720
- Hello.
- Hello.

241
00:13:55,800 --> 00:13:57,640
First take, Gluf. Action!

242
00:13:59,200 --> 00:14:01,960
He sprayed so much that it left a stain.

243
00:14:02,040 --> 00:14:03,440
He sprayed it too close.

244
00:14:03,520 --> 00:14:05,880
